1
00:00:31,070 --> 00:00:33,360
[You Have My Heart]

2
00:00:33,380 --> 00:00:36,270
[Episode 13: Hard to Deal with Evil Power]

3
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:37,200
He...

4
00:00:37,790 --> 00:00:39,070
He looked at my chest,

5
00:00:39,750 --> 00:00:42,150
saying the heart is here with me.

6
00:00:42,750 --> 00:00:44,790
I don't understand his words.

7
00:00:46,320 --> 00:00:48,430
He is using demonic words to confuse you.

8
00:00:48,430 --> 00:00:49,200
Ignore him.

9
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:54,680
Rest assured.

10
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:56,360
He can't hurt me.

11
00:00:57,790 --> 00:00:58,150
Okay.

12
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,600
I overthought it.

13
00:01:06,370 --> 00:01:08,170
The most urgent matter right now

14
00:01:08,230 --> 00:01:10,640
is that this Wish Fox is still at large.

15
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:14,490
Li Mao's tragedy is definitely
not an isolated case.

16
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:16,880
As long as he is in
Yin-Yang Crossing for a day,

17
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:19,000
more people with obsessions

18
00:01:19,340 --> 00:01:20,860
and desires

19
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:23,080
will be his targets to toy with

20
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:24,780
and even torture to death.

21
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:27,760
So, talking to him

22
00:01:28,370 --> 00:01:31,030
is the only prerequisite
for him to harm people?

23
00:01:31,150 --> 00:01:32,880
You can understand it that way.

24
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:35,220
If no one talks to him,

25
00:01:35,570 --> 00:01:37,200
or makes a wish to him,

26
00:01:37,580 --> 00:01:40,300
then he will be helpless.

27
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,680
My Lady, I have a plan.

28
00:01:42,759 --> 00:01:45,620
We can take drastic measures
and cut off the source.

29
00:01:48,050 --> 00:01:49,650
We won't issue an arrest warrant,

30
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:51,450
but the highest-level warning.

31
00:01:52,020 --> 00:01:54,140
Cooperating with Xiqianhua
and the county yamen,

32
00:01:54,140 --> 00:01:55,440
we'll post the portrait of the Wish Fox

33
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:57,500
in every corner of Yin-Yang Crossing

34
00:01:58,509 --> 00:02:00,640
to notify all the commoners and demons

35
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:02,940
that whoever sees the scholar in white

36
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:04,610
must not talk to him.

37
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,200
Go home quickly when seeing this guy.

38
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,760
Do not make eye contact with him.

39
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,560
Do not talk to him.

40
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,800
Go home quickly.

41
00:02:09,139 --> 00:02:10,130
Lock your doors and windows.

42
00:02:10,130 --> 00:02:11,660
Don't talk to this person.

43
00:02:13,710 --> 00:02:14,930
Lock your doors and windows.

44
00:02:14,930 --> 00:02:16,370
Don't talk to this person.

45
00:02:15,300 --> 00:02:16,520
[Warning]

46
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:20,240
Order all spirit envoys of Xiqianhua

47
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,460
to send orders to the demon leaders
of all regions,

48
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:24,430
telling them to restrain the demons
and spirits under their jurisdiction,

49
00:02:24,430 --> 00:02:27,750
and let them be careful with their words
and actions recently.

50
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,290
If they meet a scholar in white,

51
00:02:29,290 --> 00:02:31,350
don't have any involvement with him.

52
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:35,320
They should report to Xiqianhua
via voice transmission immediately.

53
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,320
[Xiqianhua]

54
00:02:54,410 --> 00:02:55,120
My Lord.

55
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,450
Can we really

56
00:02:56,770 --> 00:02:58,829
guard against the Wish Fox like this?

57
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,270
I don't know.

58
00:03:00,670 --> 00:03:01,600
Just do our best.

59
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:09,070
In the past, I was just an idle person,

60
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,970
I didn't feel anything.

61
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,870
After I came down the mountain
and became a constable, I realized

62
00:03:13,870 --> 00:03:15,640
that I am incompetent.

63
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:19,150
There are so many troubles
down the mountain,

64
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:21,520
yet I only thought about learning magic

65
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,320
to show off in front of everyone.

66
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:26,079
My Lord.

67
00:03:26,890 --> 00:03:28,490
Sometimes, compared to you,

68
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,390
I am indeed quite thoughtless.

69
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:35,079
Whether it's learning magic

70
00:03:35,079 --> 00:03:36,280
or being a constable,

71
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:39,350
it's all just following your own heart.

72
00:03:40,270 --> 00:03:40,800
A person

73
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,800
must first be true to himself

74
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:44,520
before he can see others.

75
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,870
Although I didn't understand,

76
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:53,000
what you said must make sense, My Lord.

77
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,620
Have a seat.

78
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:07,500
My Lady.

79
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,860
Yin-Yang Crossing

80
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:11,960
isn't just for humans.

81
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,589
When I first arrived at Yin-Yang Crossing,

82
00:04:17,589 --> 00:04:21,880
I thought morality was ruined
and laws were nonexistent here

83
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:26,390
because you used your power
to oppress the government.

84
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,390
But now,

85
00:04:30,370 --> 00:04:32,030
I'm starting to doubt myself.

86
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,430
Can I really manage this place well

87
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:37,090
with the books of sages I've read,

88
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,320
and

89
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,710
the human laws I believe in?

90
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,140
What are you afraid of?

91
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:52,230
Do what you believe in,

92
00:04:52,230 --> 00:04:53,560
and what you're good at.

93
00:04:53,790 --> 00:04:56,120
Judge fairly and accurately.

94
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:58,250
Protect the peace of the people

95
00:04:58,350 --> 00:04:59,750
within your capability.

96
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:03,980
My Lady.

97
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:08,030
Warning the people can only help them
avoid harm temporarily,

98
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:08,680
but

99
00:05:09,470 --> 00:05:11,680
how can we take the initiative
to capture him?

100
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:13,390
Leave the rest to me.

101
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:20,760
You said that

102
00:05:21,780 --> 00:05:22,980
when I'm by your side,

103
00:05:23,590 --> 00:05:26,120
your spiritual power recovers faster.

104
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,350
So, at times like this,

105
00:05:30,470 --> 00:05:32,200
don't carry it all by yourself.

106
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:36,000
I put all my trust in you.

107
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:38,420
My Lady,

108
00:05:40,260 --> 00:05:42,380
I hope I am of use to you.

109
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,320
Bai Shanjun.

110
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,860
You are useful.

111
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:55,010
It's because you are so useful

112
00:05:56,030 --> 00:05:56,909
that I hope

113
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:59,090
I can keep you safe.

114
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,390
Grinding it every day,

115
00:06:34,909 --> 00:06:36,790
you're going to grind this knife thin.

116
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:37,710
The shop has been closed for a day.

117
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:39,110
We've lost so much money.

118
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:41,080
When will these awful days end?

119
00:06:41,230 --> 00:06:42,960
Just listen to Lady Fufeng.

120
00:06:43,710 --> 00:06:44,909
It's for our own good.

121
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,560
Who is it?

122
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,420
Hurry up and go inside.

123
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:57,360
Who is it?

124
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:58,830
Have mercy.

125
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,420
I'm a passerby.

126
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:02,080
I ran into a wolf in the mountains

127
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,140
and injured my leg.

128
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,900
I just want a bowl of water.

129
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,470
Fufeng.

130
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,270
So heartless.

131
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:30,210
We haven't seen each other for years,

132
00:07:30,590 --> 00:07:32,920
and you're guarding against me like this.

133
00:07:51,590 --> 00:07:52,080
Master.

134
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,350
I just received a report
from a demon leader.

135
00:07:55,350 --> 00:07:56,150
In the South Alley,

136
00:07:56,150 --> 00:07:58,960
a broom spirit who hasn't taken human form
sent a message,

137
00:07:58,960 --> 00:07:59,560
saying

138
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:01,390
that two hours ago

139
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,890
he saw a woodcutter.

140
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,270
It was suspected to be Wish Fox
in disguise.

141
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:07,120
But that thing came and left
without a trace

142
00:08:07,120 --> 00:08:08,980
and didn't leak any demonic aura.

143
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,030
It is really hard to track.

144
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:16,270
I didn't expect that after seventy years,

145
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,700
he hasn't repented at all,

146
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:20,430
and his methods have become
even more secretive.

147
00:08:20,790 --> 00:08:21,320
Master,

148
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,920
is it because

149
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:26,440
you've consumed too much
spiritual power lately,

150
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,640
and the seal loosened

151
00:08:27,910 --> 00:08:28,510
that he has

152
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:31,200
an opportunity to exploit?

153
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:33,570
Not to that extent.

154
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:35,320
Someone

155
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:37,440
helped him from the outside.

156
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,740
So, he opened part of the seal.

157
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,590
Bai Han?

158
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,000
By the way,

159
00:08:44,350 --> 00:08:44,810
Master,

160
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:46,960
I just checked the secret room.

161
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:50,040
The five hundred demon hearts
sealed in the secret room

162
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,770
are all gone.

163
00:08:59,570 --> 00:09:02,810
If all of them are devoured by him…

164
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:15,110
The Five Hundred Demon Hearts Massacre.

165
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:16,440
Wish Fox, a half-demon,

166
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:18,970
within 21 days,

167
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:21,680
slaughtered five hundred demons
and took all their hearts.

168
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:23,280
Liu Fufeng bound him,

169
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,110
and sealed him in Xiqianhua,

170
00:09:25,110 --> 00:09:27,440
along with the five hundred demon hearts.

171
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:36,900
My Lord.

172
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:38,870
I've patrolled the streets

173
00:09:38,870 --> 00:09:40,800
and haven't found anything
unusual for now.

174
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,400
The refugees and beggars on the street

175
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,830
have also been settled
by your wishes.

176
00:09:43,830 --> 00:09:44,320
Good.

177
00:09:45,110 --> 00:09:46,240
Come and take a look.

178
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:50,400
Do you know about the Five Hundred
Demon Hearts Massacre?

179
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:51,200
Oh, this case.

180
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:51,830
I know.

181
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:56,000
This incident happened seventy years ago.

182
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,830
It's about Lady Fufeng's

183
00:09:58,990 --> 00:10:00,050
romantic history.

184
00:10:00,990 --> 00:10:02,050
Romantic history?

185
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,160
Don't talk nonsense.

186
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,280
It's true.

187
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:09,960
It is said that back then, a fox demon

188
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:12,510
admired Lady Fufeng so much

189
00:10:12,510 --> 00:10:13,830
that he went crazy.

190
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,760
He thought demon hearts were great tonics,

191
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:19,560
so he sneaked around and dug out
five hundred demon hearts,

192
00:10:19,560 --> 00:10:21,800
offering them to Lady Fufeng
as a tonic to show his love.

193
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:22,870
But Lady Fufeng

194
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,350
couldn't tolerate his behavior.

195
00:10:24,350 --> 00:10:26,710
She personally sealed this demon.

196
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,230
Wish Fox

197
00:10:33,250 --> 00:10:36,590
[The tragedy of 500 demons' hearts]

198
00:10:33,770 --> 00:10:35,110
is the demon.

199
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:38,510
Really?

200
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,350
Yes,

201
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,590
it's him.

202
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,410
Oh no. We're doomed.

203
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:45,710
That demon has been sealed
for seventy years.

204
00:10:45,710 --> 00:10:46,510
If he breaks the seal,

205
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:48,310
he must hate Lady Fufeng deeply.

206
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,350
We have to quickly think of a way

207
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:51,480
to help Lady Fufeng.

208
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,740
What about this case file?

209
00:10:53,870 --> 00:10:55,470
It's recorded too briefly.

210
00:10:56,080 --> 00:10:58,320
We need to know more clearly,

211
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:00,690
so we can help her at critical moments.

212
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:01,440
Keep looking.

213
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:03,640
There must be more detailed files here.

214
00:11:22,890 --> 00:11:29,130
[Zuiwang Tavern]

215
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,510
Wish Fox

216
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:08,020
is a half-demon.

217
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:09,870
His mother was a fox.

218
00:12:10,090 --> 00:12:12,160
She died of dystocia
on the day he was born.

219
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:14,750
His human father saw him as an ill omen

220
00:12:14,750 --> 00:12:16,700
and abandoned him
in the wilderness as a baby.

221
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:18,300
He grew up alone in the street

222
00:12:18,500 --> 00:12:20,250
and later worked
as a servant at Zuiwang Tavern.

223
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:22,850
Due to his half-demon body
and weak nature,

224
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,800
he was heavily bullied.

225
00:12:25,110 --> 00:12:26,230
Let me wipe it for you,

226
00:12:26,230 --> 00:12:26,590
sir.

227
00:12:26,820 --> 00:12:27,620
Let me wipe it.

228
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,600
Little bastard, are you blind?

229
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:32,950
I know I was wrong, sir. I...

230
00:12:33,930 --> 00:12:34,870
I was wrong.

231
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:35,870
Bastard!

232
00:12:36,510 --> 00:12:37,510
Let me take a look.

233
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,370
Little bastard.

234
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,330
You little bastard!

235
00:12:43,520 --> 00:12:44,920
I'll beat you to death!

236
00:12:45,290 --> 00:12:46,350
You deserve to be bullied.

237
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:47,280
Little bastard!

238
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:48,890
Little bastard!

239
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:51,320
You spineless coward. Do you yield?

240
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:53,330
His aura is strange.

241
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:55,350
That suppressed resentment

242
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:59,080
is mixed with a talent
for twisting wishes,

243
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:02,210
like a young beast hiding venomous fangs.

244
00:13:02,340 --> 00:13:03,400
If left unchecked,

245
00:13:03,870 --> 00:13:05,510
I'm afraid he will become
a source of evil.

246
00:13:05,510 --> 00:13:08,160
Liu Fufeng worried about
his long-accumulated resentment,

247
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,990
fearing he would fall into an evil path,

248
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:10,960
so she brought him to Xiqianhua.

249
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:11,620
Stop!

250
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:15,110
She intended to guide him towards
goodness and the right path.

251
00:13:19,040 --> 00:13:20,230
From today on,

252
00:13:20,970 --> 00:13:22,630
I will bring you to Xiqianhua.

253
00:13:43,620 --> 00:13:44,780
Why are you here?

254
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:53,040
Didn't I send you to
the demon academy to study?

255
00:13:53,050 --> 00:13:54,310
Why did you sneak back?

256
00:13:54,590 --> 00:13:55,520
Skipping class?

257
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:58,040
I just want to

258
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,860
serve you forever.

259
00:14:01,920 --> 00:14:02,800
Little fox.

260
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:05,910
No one will bully you again,

261
00:14:06,470 --> 00:14:08,870
and you don't have
to serve anyone anymore.

262
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,200
Cultivate well.

263
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,480
In the future,

264
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:12,990
you can do whatever

265
00:14:13,510 --> 00:14:14,470
you want.

266
00:14:16,110 --> 00:14:16,920
I...

267
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:20,750
I just want to stay by your side

268
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:23,160
and fulfill all of your wishes.

269
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,920
Your eyes

270
00:14:49,230 --> 00:14:50,710
are quite clear.

271
00:15:10,790 --> 00:15:12,240
I was just praising them.

272
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:13,600
What are you doing?

273
00:15:13,850 --> 00:15:15,450
You said they are beautiful.

274
00:15:15,540 --> 00:15:17,130
Doesn't it mean you want to have them?

275
00:15:17,130 --> 00:15:18,110
Whatever you want,

276
00:15:18,110 --> 00:15:19,440
I will give it to you.

277
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:20,750
Whatever I don't have,

278
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,480
I will definitely find for you.

279
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:27,720
My God.

280
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:30,460
He doesn't look like a normal one.

281
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:31,230
No.

282
00:15:31,350 --> 00:15:33,710
He is not a normal demon
from the very beginning.

283
00:15:33,710 --> 00:15:35,870
However, his nature was already set,

284
00:15:36,070 --> 00:15:38,420
and cultivation had little effect.

285
00:15:39,310 --> 00:15:41,640
As long as that half heart doesn't return,

286
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,200
your heart

287
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:44,960
will never be stable.

288
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:48,990
Heart.

289
00:15:51,510 --> 00:15:52,320
Fufeng

290
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:55,010
needs a heart.

291
00:15:56,320 --> 00:16:00,060
Later, he accidentally learned the secret
that Fufeng had lost half of her heart.

292
00:16:00,060 --> 00:16:01,180
Within 21 days,

293
00:16:01,680 --> 00:16:03,080
he killed five hundred demons

294
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,560
and took all their hearts.

295
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:16,520
This demon feeds on wishes.

296
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:18,200
It's inherently evil.

297
00:16:22,810 --> 00:16:24,400
Has she always been

298
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:25,960
facing all this alone?

299
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:33,310
My Lord, Constable Chen.

300
00:16:34,780 --> 00:16:35,590
Why panic?

301
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:36,680
What happened?

302
00:16:36,970 --> 00:16:37,490
My Lord,

303
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:38,880
we have patrolled the city.

304
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:39,920
Nothing unusual so far.

305
00:16:39,920 --> 00:16:42,320
But there's a situation at Zuiwang Tavern.

306
00:16:42,590 --> 00:16:43,470
Zuiwang Tavern?

307
00:16:43,470 --> 00:16:43,990
Yes.

308
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,460
Lady Fufeng went there

309
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:46,230
and dismissed

310
00:16:46,230 --> 00:16:48,090
all the staff staying overnight.

311
00:16:48,190 --> 00:16:49,160
Right now, she is alone

312
00:16:49,160 --> 00:16:50,490
drinking in the tavern.

313
00:16:52,350 --> 00:16:53,280
Zuiwang Tavern.

314
00:16:54,450 --> 00:16:56,110
That was where they first met.

315
00:16:57,370 --> 00:16:58,700
She was waiting for him.

316
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:01,440
I have a new wish.

317
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:02,700
Are you

318
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:05,079
still unwilling to show yourself?

319
00:17:10,790 --> 00:17:11,510
What?

320
00:17:12,710 --> 00:17:14,440
You swallowed 500 demon hearts

321
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:16,109
and strengthened your body,

322
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:19,880
but you don't even have the courage
to come out and see me?

323
00:17:19,990 --> 00:17:20,790
Fufeng.

324
00:17:22,050 --> 00:17:24,359
I stayed in that dark jar

325
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:26,119
for 70 whole years.

326
00:17:26,119 --> 00:17:27,410
70 years.

327
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,840
I prayed for you every day,

328
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:31,550
hoping you could get your heart back.

329
00:17:31,550 --> 00:17:32,610
But what about you?

330
00:17:32,810 --> 00:17:34,010
All you want

331
00:17:34,430 --> 00:17:37,360
is to catch me and lock me up again.

332
00:17:37,380 --> 00:17:38,450
Right?

333
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:40,030
Wish Fox.

334
00:17:40,230 --> 00:17:41,830
You slaughtered 500 demons.

335
00:17:42,020 --> 00:17:44,620
By law, your body and spirit
should be refined.

336
00:17:45,030 --> 00:17:47,270
I sealed your spirit in the jar

337
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:49,400
just to see

338
00:17:50,230 --> 00:17:52,960
if time could make you understand that

339
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:55,560
those beating in the chests you cut open

340
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:58,390
are not just tonics

341
00:17:59,090 --> 00:18:01,090
but living lives.

342
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:03,960
I know I was wrong.

343
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,340
I will never harm anyone again.

344
00:18:06,340 --> 00:18:07,670
As for the child, Li Mao,

345
00:18:07,990 --> 00:18:09,030
I just saw

346
00:18:09,600 --> 00:18:10,990
my past self in him.

347
00:18:11,600 --> 00:18:12,360
He was so weak

348
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:13,550
and helpless.

349
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:15,120
That's why I helped him once.

350
00:18:15,120 --> 00:18:16,450
I will never do it again.

351
00:18:19,810 --> 00:18:20,570
Lady Fufeng.

352
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:22,620
Can you trust me once again

353
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:23,920
like before?

354
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:30,840
Then tell me.

355
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:33,330
What did you promise the person

356
00:18:33,930 --> 00:18:35,100
who rescued you?

357
00:18:35,990 --> 00:18:36,880
There is no one else.

358
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:38,010
There is no one else.

359
00:18:38,310 --> 00:18:39,070
It was me.

360
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:41,070
I really wanted to see you.

361
00:18:42,130 --> 00:18:43,160
I didn't betray you.

362
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:44,270
And I never will.

363
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,040
I thought

364
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:51,440
all living things could be saved.

365
00:18:52,790 --> 00:18:53,590
But I

366
00:18:55,150 --> 00:18:56,080
cannot save you.

367
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:05,960
I told you she didn't need you.

368
00:19:06,640 --> 00:19:08,810
Why did you beg like a dog?

369
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:12,240
Offer yourself to me.

370
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:28,440
Lady Fufeng.

371
00:19:31,990 --> 00:19:32,640
Look.

372
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,400
I have refined their hearts

373
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,750
altogether.

374
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,490
It is strong enough

375
00:19:40,400 --> 00:19:42,360
to make up for your missing half.

376
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:44,360
This way,

377
00:19:45,710 --> 00:19:47,240
you can be powerful forever

378
00:19:48,870 --> 00:19:50,740
and stay with me forever.

379
00:19:52,230 --> 00:19:54,230
My heart is with Yin-Yang Crossing.

380
00:19:54,550 --> 00:19:56,010
I don't care about petty romance.

381
00:19:56,010 --> 00:19:58,010
Nor would I have any involvement

382
00:19:59,210 --> 00:20:00,620
with a monster like you.

383
00:20:06,550 --> 00:20:07,600
Fine.

384
00:20:10,360 --> 00:20:11,550
If you need it,

385
00:20:13,910 --> 00:20:15,220
then take it.

386
00:20:27,480 --> 00:20:28,410
Fufeng,

387
00:20:30,690 --> 00:20:31,860
you're too cruel.

388
00:21:01,970 --> 00:21:02,970
Lady Fufeng.

389
00:21:03,870 --> 00:21:04,720
Bai Shanjun.

390
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:22,790
Fufeng,

391
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:26,200
every time we met,

392
00:21:26,840 --> 00:21:28,120
we ended up fighting.

393
00:21:29,580 --> 00:21:32,790
You didn't even give me
a moment to catch up.

394
00:21:33,270 --> 00:21:33,960
This time,

395
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:37,030
let's have a good talk.

